CROSS-EXAMINATION 
Witness: Dr. R.S. Patil

Q: Did the contract not state that the contractor must satisfy themselves of the site conditions?
A: It did, but it is technically impossible for a contractor to do 50 deep boreholes in a 21-day tender period. We relied on the Department's geological report, which formed part of the contract data.

Q: Are you aware this is a "Lump Sum" contract?
A: No, this is an item-rate contract based on BoQ.
